snippet.title: PUSH THE MAAX with Maax - Episode 5: Truth
snippet.description:
In this episode, I talk about the importance of looking at things objectively and refraining from letting your feelings or bias get in the way.
A real warrior looks at things using critical thinking and forms conclusions based on fact. A bottom feeder only discerns things based on emotion and feeling, discarding fact.
I use two cases to exemplify this: the case involving Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, and the case involving Evan Rachel Wood and Marilyn Manson.
